# .env.local - Local Development (Python without Docker)
# Copy .env to .env.local for running Python directly on your Mac
#
# Usage:
#   cp .env .env.local
#   python pkm-bridge-server.py  # Uses .env.local if it exists, else .env
#
# For Docker testing:
#   Use .env with your Mac paths (for volume mounts)
#   Inside container, paths are overridden to /data/org-agenda and /data/logseq
#
# NOTE: .env.local is gitignored
